headline: Barclays Lowers EOG Resources (EOG) PT to $136, Cites Broader Oil and E&P Sector Cuts
summary: EOG Resources Inc. (NYSE:EOG) is one of the best value stocks to invest in now. On October 7, Barclays lowered the firm’s price target on EOG Resources to $136 from $140, while keeping an Equal Weight rating on the shares.
